Description: Alienware AlienFX Light Manipulation Program
 The AlienFX feature is available on some AlienWare computers. This program
 enables the ability to change the lights to any RGB value and also to turn
 the lights off completely.  A 4096-colour RGB palette is supported with
 commands to Morph between colours, blinking and fixed colours.  Multiple
 lightchip models are known and supported.
